The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 BCCI meeting next month

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: The BCCI will hold a meeting next month to discuss its proposed high profile Twenty20 League. Foreigners may also be asked to participate, said secretary Niranjan Shah. 

All I can say is it is at an early stage The idea was floated last year. The modalities will be discussed at a meeting next month and we could have foreign players participating, he said. 




